 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {"id": "title"},
   "source": [
    "# 🔍 MLOps Monitoring Pipeline — Estrategia de Monitoreo E2E\n",
    "\n",
    "**Tarea del curso Machine Learning Operations**\n",
    "\n",
    "## Arquitectura del pipeline de monitoreo\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "Prefect Flow: monitoring_pipeline(payload)\n",
    "│\n",
    "├── [PARALELO CPU — 2+ workers]\n",
    "│   ├── task: compute_raw_drift          → PSI sobre datos crudos\n",
    "│   ├── task: compute_preprocessed_drift → PSI sobre datos preprocesados\n",
    "│   ├── task: compute_score_drift        → PSI sobre scores puros\n",
    "│   └── task: compute_postprocessed_drift→ PSI sobre scores posprocesados\n",
    "│\n",
    "├── task: compute_shap_task             → SHAP importance (paralelismo CPU)\n",
    "├── task: update_shap_history           → Historial mes a mes\n",
    "├── task: save_monitoring_results       → Persistencia CSV/JSON\n",
    "└── task: generate_dashboard_task       → Tablero HTML interactivo\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "## Payload\n",
    "```python\n",
    "payload = {\n",
    "    'DIR_RAWDATA'       : '/ruta/datos_crudos',         # CSV con datos de entrada\n",
    "    'DIR_REF_RAWDATA'   : '/ruta/referencia_crudos',    # CSV de referencia (mes base)\n",
    "    'DIR_PROCESSED'     : '/ruta/datos_preprocesados',  # salida de preprocessing.py\n",
    "    'DIR_REF_PROCESSED' : '/ruta/referencia_preprocesados',\n",
    "    'SCORE_DIR'         : '/ruta/scores_puros',         # salida de inference.py\n",
    "    'DIR_REF_SCORES'    : '/ruta/referencia_scores',\n",
    "    'DIR_OUTPUT'        : '/ruta/scores_posprocesados', # salida de posprocessing.py\n",
    "    'DIR_REF_OUTPUT'    : '/ruta/referencia_posprocesados',\n",
    "    'MODEL_DIR'         : '/ruta/modelos',              # directorio del model registry\n",
    "    'MONITORING_DIR'    : '/ruta/monitoring',           # directorio de salidas de monitoreo\n",
    "    'SHAP_HISTORY_PATH' : '/ruta/monitoring/shap_history.json',\n",
    "    'params': {\n",
    "        'model_name' : 'extrac',\n",
    "        'partition'  : 10,\n",
    "        'dd_metric'  : 'PSI',    # 'PSI' o 'KL'\n",
    "        'quantils'   : 10,\n",
    "        'n_workers'  : 2,        # mínimo 2 (paralelismo CPU)\n",
    "        'shap_sample': 500\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n"
   ]
  },
  {
